    "types": [
      "Conviction"
    ],
    "card_text": "When an effect that would change control of this imbued is played or announced, you may burn this card to cancel that effect. Burn this card to cancel either an action directed at this imbued that requires Chimerstry [chi], Dementation [dem], Dominate [dom], Presence [pre], or Serpentis [ser] or a strike card that requires any of those Disciplines played by a minion opposing this imbued as it is announced. No cost is paid.",
