    ],
    "ordered_sets": [
      "Nights of Reckoning"
    ],
    "legality": "2006-04-10",
    "rulings": [
      {
        "text": "If used to cancel an action, the action is not performed, the minion stays unlocked (and can try the same action again). [LSJ 20060425]",
        "references": [
          {
            "text": "[LSJ 20060425]",
            "label": "LSJ 20060425",
            "url": "https://groups.google.com/g/rec.games.trading-cards.jyhad/c/U34QDob4Vco/m/hcaMIn9W88kJ"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "If used to cancel a {Corruption} action, then the action is canceled in its entirety and the corruption counters are not burned. [LSJ 20070222-1]",
        "references": [
          {
            "text": "[LSJ 20070222-1]",
            "label": "LSJ 20070222-1",
            "url": "https://groups.google.com/g/rec.games.trading-cards.jyhad/c/jBrfK77gayo/m/fnk0EgSpN8AJ"
          }
        ],
        "cards": [
          {
            "text": "{Corruption}",
            "id": 100430,
            "name": "Corruption",
            "usual_name": "Corruption",
            "vekn_name": "Corruption"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "If the canceled card had a \"Do Not Replace Until\" clause on it, that clause is canceled as well and the card is replaced normally. [LSJ 20011023]",
        "references": [
          {
            "text": "[LSJ 20011023]",
            "label": "LSJ 20011023",
            "url": "https://groups.google.com/g/rec.games.trading-cards.jyhad/c/2GOLIrXAF8M/m/P4T3Dj6UNL0J"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Can be used to cancel all action cards, including employ retainer, recruit ally and political action. [ANK 20200813-2]",
        "references": [
          {
            "text": "[ANK 20200813-2]",
            "label": "ANK 20200813-2",
            "url": "https://www.vekn.net/forum/rules-questions/78799-rewind-time-inf-and-action-cards#100526"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "The ability to fail an action must be used before action modifiers or reactions that are not explicitly played \"as the action is announced\". [ANK 20190425]",
        "references": [
          {
            "text": "[ANK 20190425]",
